flowchart LR
    Ref["ref clock"] --> PLL["PLL"]
    PLL --> Mux["glitchless mux"]
    Mux --> Div["divider"]
    Div --> Gate["clock gate"]
    Gate --> Domain["GPU clock domain"]

    FW["FW DVFS FSM"] -->|program + wait ack| PLL
    FW -->|select clock path| Mux
    FW -->|update divider| Div
    FW -->|enable/disable| Gate
    FW -->|release only after stable| Domain
